Pan-fry or grill 6 links Aidells Smoked Chicken and Apple Sausages for about 10 minutes until lightly browned. Meanwhile, in a 2-cup bowl, combine 3/4 cup chopped tomato, 3 tablespoons balsamic vinegar, 1/3 cup olive oil, and 3 tablespoons chopped fresh basil. Cut cooked sausage links into 3/4-inch-thick chunks. Just before serving, top baguette slices with a spoonful of the tomato mixture and a slice of sausage.